      <title>创建 Hexo 项目</title>
      <link href="/2025/05/27/Pages/"/>
      <url>/2025/05/27/Pages/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="创建-Hexo-项目"><a href="#创建-Hexo-项目" class="headerlink" title="创建 Hexo 项目"></a>创建 Hexo 项目</h1><ol><li>请在命令行中进入到你想创建项目的目录（例如 E:\y1y\），然后执行以下命令：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init .</span><br><span class="line">hexo install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>修改 _config.yml</li></ol><p>打开 Hexo 项目的 _config.yml 文件，进行以下配置：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Site</span><br><span class="line">title: Uneac1</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">description: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">author: Uneac1</span><br><span class="line">language: zh-CN</span><br><span class="line">timezone: &#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># URL</span><br><span class="line">url: https://y130.icu</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># ... existing code ...</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Deployment</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com:UNEAC1/UNEAC1.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装-hexo-deployer-git-插件"><a href="#安装-hexo-deployer-git-插件" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo-deployer-git 插件"></a>安装 hexo-deployer-git 插件</h1><ol><li>在命令行中执行以下命令安装部署插件：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd e:/y1y/x</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>配置 Git 全局信息</li></ol><p>使用以下命令配置你的 Git 用户信息：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;Uneac1&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;1006849568@qq.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>安装 Hexo 所需的依赖</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li>启动 SSH 代理</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eval $(ssh-agent -s)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ssh-add E:/yil/yy130</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="5"><li>测试连接</li></ol><ul><li>使用以下命令测试是否可以成功连接 GitHub：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>如果一切设置正确，GitHub 会回复：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hi your_username! You&#x27;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="生成-public"><a href="#生成-public" class="headerlink" title="生成 public"></a>生成 public</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>初始化git仓库：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>链接到远程仓库：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote add origin git@github.com:Uneac1/repo.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>提交git：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;LOL1&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li>推送：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push -u origin main</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="5"><li>创建并生成main：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git checkout -b main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="刷新-Hexo"><a href="#刷新-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="刷新 Hexo"></a>刷新 Hexo</h1><ul><li>如果你修改了主题的样式，别忘了刷新 Hexo：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>生成静态文件并部署：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="关于图片"><a href="#关于图片" class="headerlink" title="关于图片"></a>关于图片</h1><ul><li>使用本地图片</li></ul><p>将图片保存到 Hexo 项目的 source&#x2F;images 文件夹中，并使用相对路径来引用它。例如，假设你将图片命名为 logo.png，你可以这样引用：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![Hexo Logo](/images/logo.png)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>使用网络图片</li></ul><p>如果你希望使用外部 URL 的图片，确保 URL 地址有效并且可以访问。例如：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![Hexo Logo](https://hexo.io/images/logo.png)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果仍然无法加载，建议检查网络连接或者确保图片的 URL 地址正确。你也可以尝试将图片下载到本地并上传到博客的图片目录。</p><ul><li>设置封面图片</li></ul><p>在 Hexo 中设置封面图片，可以通过修改配置文件或在文章的 Front Matter 中指定封面图片。以下是几种常见的设置封面图片的方法：</p><ul><li>在 _config.yml 文件中设置封面</li></ul><p>如果你想为整个网站设置默认的封面图片，可以在 Hexo 的 _config.yml 文件中添加一行代码：</p><p>这是主题设置的部分，可能会有所不同，具体取决于你的主题</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cover:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  image: /images/cover.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>确保图片已经放在 source&#x2F;images 文件夹下，或者直接使用外部 URL。</p><ul><li>在文章 Front Matter 中设置封面</li></ul><p>如果你想为某篇文章单独设置封面图片，可以在该文章的 Front Matter（文章头部元数据）中添加封面图片的路径。示例如下：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 我的文章标题</span><br><span class="line">date: 2025-05-27</span><br><span class="line">cover: /images/cover.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
